{"tid":1683141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【黃店勝利戰線】一齊話比播TVB店主知：將視為深藍","createTime":"2019-10-30T13:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:50:28.000Z","uid":280192,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8daccc4e710b9fd52c6cc18441e64a3c61be90","tid":1683141,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"知道好多手足，心裡已有呢個判斷。<br />\n<br />\n播TVB就係代表藍，問題係：d店主唔知。<br />\n<br />\n請明確比呢類餐廳知道：&ldquo;老細，網上d人講緊話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB餐廳唔幫襯！</span></span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n佢地不知不覺幫手洗左一代人嘅腦。唔可以比佢地無代價咁洗多一代。<br />\n<br />\n如果肯轉，不妨考慮食。<br />\n<br />\n否則，大家可以公開：已忠告但繼續播TVB的舖頭，呢堆TVB爪牙將成為黃店長勝戰線中，下一批大輸家。"},{"pid":"091aad00d9fe75f46bb07f68f2e153802a1042d4","tid":1683141,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa5f2efa9525811a947e6d681f9da9be4d67c01","tid":1683141,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807af2c5e8b225fe0b536bf5c6460cd0b1a88be8","tid":1683141,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:15:17.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cff5f798121a0887d732d79514c45b4edb41f29","tid":1683141,"uid":288199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579ae6de411c35641da03756254cbb3e246dd7ea","tid":1683141,"uid":313959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T20:47:16.000Z","msg":"睇TVB唔代表撐藍色喎，如果店主冇話撐藍色，你地只係干預佢睇電視嘅自由，咁樣做同大陸收緊我哋嘅自由有咩唔同呀。我贊成唔幫襯支持藍色嘅小店，但千祈唔好殺錯淺黃嘅自己人。"},{"pid":"b47263e10f161c78fdb2b56b4ab50580ac5e827a","tid":1683141,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa2541616a419a753b9e27856558580724e9bea","tid":1683141,"uid":312598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:35:09.000Z","msg":"睇左幾個月假新聞黃極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd29577a236e97ef931215d5bc06bae1df3521a","tid":1683141,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"播TVB都唔食<br />\n由7月開始已經係"}]}